name: NBI Unconstrained Fixed Income ETF
longDescription: The NBI Unconstrained Fixed Income ETF's investment objective is to maximize total return, consistent with preservation of capital. Fune invests, directly or indirectly through investments in securities of one or many other mutual funds or through the use of derivatives, in a diversified portfolio composed mainly of fixed-income securities of issuers located throughout the world with various maturities and credit ratings.
